05T04:14:43.000Z","msg":"曾帶車路士三奪英超冠軍的摩連奴，又指利物浦餘下的比賽都會將曼城放在心內：「曼城位列榜首，已將命運掌握在手裏，利物浦卻失去控制。利物浦不能再只想着自己去比賽，他們腦海中每周將有兩場賽事：自己的比賽和曼城的。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fe8c32dc3b69152ec1c11265e95c6bc3c9531f","tid":1046281,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19ac6c0bda3790bd4d7e1a323c3ee22acb33be1","tid":1046281,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"「曼城敗了，但當利物浦和波他們又會得到正能量。」<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪撈埋風水師，正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"其實兩隊個擺位調轉都係一樣意思<br />\n講黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210ef3d267d6b40fd05f88990294bfae1e047e89","tid":1046281,"uid":82304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"852250a0708823b768ad4d8edc07e23bfead4ebb","tid":1046281,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"頂級領隊講波係唔同D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"條友係講到有咩問題出嚟 但自己唔會做先on9"}]}